quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Did We not open your breast for you
  94,2,and relieve you of your burden
  94,3,"which [almost] broke your back"
  94,4,Did We not exalt your name
  94,5,Indeed ease accompanies hardship
  94,6,Indeed ease accompanies hardship
  94,7,"So when you are done, appoint"
  94,8,and supplicate your Lord